net.bytebuddy.asm

Class Advice.Dispatcher.Active.CodeTranslationVisitor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.objectweb.asm.MethodVisitor
      • net.bytebuddy.asm.Advice.Dispatcher.Active.CodeTranslationVisitor
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Advice.Dispatcher.Active.CodeTranslationVisitor.ReturnValueDiscarding, Advice.Dispatcher.Active.CodeTranslationVisitor.ReturnValueRetaining
    Enclosing class:
    Advice.Dispatcher.Active

    protected abstract static class Advice.Dispatcher.Active.CodeTranslationVisitor
extends MethodVisitor
    A visitor for translating an advise method's byte code for inlining into the instrumented method.
